I '''Christopher Columbus''' (pilatan ning [[August 25]] ampong [[October 31]], [[1451]] – [[May 20]], [[1506]]), '''Cristóbal Colón''' king Castila, at '''Cristoforo Colombo''' king orihinal a Italianu, metung yang talapaglayag, kolonialista, ampong talapaglakbe. Uli ning kayang pamaglakbe king [[Atlantic Ocean]], akilala de reng keraklan king [[Europa]] ing Albugang Kapitnang-Yatu (Western Hemisphere) ampo reng [[w:America (continent)|kontinenting America]]. Lipat ning aliwa ya ing mumunang miras karing Americas manibat king [[Afro-Eurasia]]{{mdash}}aunahan neng manga limang dalang banuang [[Leif Ericson]], at [[Pre-Columbian trans-oceanic contact|mapaliaring deng aliwa]]{{mdash}}inumpisan nang Columbus ing maleparan a pamiugnayan da reng [[Demography of Europe|Europeo]] ampo reng [[w:Indigenous peoples of the Americas|tubu kareng Americas]]. Inumpisan na king kayang e matagumpeng pamagtangkang mitátag tuknangan o balayán (''settlement'') king isla ning [[Hispaniola]] ing prosesu ning pamaniakup da reng Castila king "[[Bayung Yatu]]" (New World). (Gagamitan de ing katayang "[[w:pre-Columbian|pre-Columbian]]" ba rong tulduan deng kultura ampong lahi kareng Americas bayu ing paniatang da ri Columbus ampo reng Europeong minalili kaya.)
           
